Bryan Santana of Orlando murdered his roommate Shelby Fazio in October last year . 
  He was found guilty of first-degree murder on Thursday and sentenced to two life terms in prison . 
  The 20-year-old stabbed and strangled her to death and sexually abused her corpse . 
  He also killed her dog and wrote messages in blood on the wall of their home . 
  Santana was also charged with attempted murder for stabbing his second roommate with a knife . 
  Judge Renee Roche said he has 'no glimmer of humanity'